                    <h1
                        class="font-crimson text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-[#9c2756] font-bold tracking-[6px] sm:tracking-[8px] uppercase"
                        id="titulo"
                    >
                        Mis XV Años
                    </h1>

                    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mt-1">
                        <div
                            class="h-px w-12 sm:w-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-[#c9973a]"
